# MiOS -- Cursor agent entry point.
#
# The locally hosted MiOS AI models orchestrate all work in this stack.
# Cursor routes through MIOS_AI_ENDPOINT=http://localhost:8080/v1 (the
# OpenAI-compatible local endpoint) and defers to those models. Strict
# adherence to OpenAI API standards and patterns -- no vendor-native
# protocols, no proprietary side-channels.
#
# Canonical prompt: /usr/share/mios/ai/system.md (deployed from mios-bootstrap).
# Apply /etc/mios/ai/system-prompt.md as host-local override if present.
# Apply ~/.config/mios/system-prompt.md as per-user override if present.
